quote.summary: Hangzhou Sf Intra-City Industrial Co Ltd is a China-based company principally engaged in the intra-city on-demand delivery services. The Company, along with its subsidiaries, provides both intra-city delivery for merchants and consumers and last-mile delivery mainly for logistics companies. The Company has adopted a multi-scenario business model featuring full coverage of delivery scenarios for all types of products and services. The Company's service coverage, ranging from mature scenarios such as food delivery to growth scenarios including local retail, local e-commerce and local services, has enabled us to respond to the evolving customer needs brought about by the development and upgrade of the local consumer market. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in the domestic market.
